      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most meticulous inspection. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, and its condition reflects a life of pampered ownership. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like shine with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections; it has recently been treated with a multi-year ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the interior remains in 'time-capsule' condition. The premium leather seating surfaces show no signs of entry wear or creasing, the dashboard is pristine with no UV fading, and the original factory scent remains. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate climate control sensors, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. The engine bay is detailed to a high standard, showing no fluid seepage or hardware oxidation. It comes with a comprehensive service dossier documenting every fluid change and inspection since new, along with two sets of original keys and all factory literature. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that looks, feels, and drives as if it just left the dealership floor.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
